item.description:
Gabriel came and asked, &ldquo;What is faith?&rdquo; Allah&rsquo;s Messenger replied, &lsquo;Faith is to believe in Allah, His angels, (the) meeting with Him, His Apostles, and to believe in Resurrection.&quot;
Then he further asked, &ldquo;What is Islam?&rdquo; Allah&rsquo;s Messenger replied, &ldquo;To worship Allah Alone and none else, to offer prayers perfectly, to pay the compulsory charity (Zakat) and to observe fasts during the month of Ramadan.&rdquo;
Then he further asked, &ldquo;What is Ihsan (perfection)?
